        "title": "Challenge-based learning",
        "text": "Challenge-based learning (CBL) is a framework for learning while solving real-world Challenges. The framework is collaborative and hands-on, asking all participants (students, teachers, families, and community members) to identify Big Ideas, ask good questions, discover and solve Challenges, gain in-depth subject area knowledge, develop 21st-century skills, and share their thoughts with the world - [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Challenge-based_learning wikipedia]"
